ZH: 我们学校的舍监非常负责。
EN: The dormitory supervisor at our school is very responsible.

ZH: 请务必向舍监报备离校时间。
EN: Please remember to inform the dormitory supervisor of your departure time.

ZH: 舍监每晚都会巡视宿舍楼。
EN: The dormitory supervisor patrols the dormitory building every night.

ZH: 舍监会帮助学生解决宿舍生活中的问题。
EN: The dormitory supervisor helps students resolve issues in dormitory life.

ZH: 如果有任何紧急情况，请立即寻求舍监的帮助。
EN: If there is any emergency, please seek assistance from the dormitory supervisor immediately.

ZH: 舍监负责宿舍楼的安全和秩序。
EN: The dormitory supervisor is responsible for the safety and order of the dormitory building.

ZH: 学生需要遵守舍监的规定和管理。
EN: Students are required to abide by the regulations and management of the dormitory supervisor.

ZH: 舍监会定期举行宿舍楼会议。
EN: The dormitory supervisor holds regular meetings for the dormitory building.

ZH: 学生可以向舍监提出关于宿舍设施的建议。
EN: Students can provide suggestions on dormitory facilities to the dormitory supervisor.

ZH: 舍监会帮助新生适应宿舍生活。
EN: The dormitory supervisor assists freshmen in adapting to dormitory life.

ZH: 舍监能提供宿舍卫生方面的指导和帮助。
EN: The dormitory supervisor can provide guidance and assistance in dormitory hygiene.

ZH: 学生要保持与舍监的良好沟通。
EN: Students should maintain good communication with the dormitory supervisor.

ZH: 舍监会检查宿舍楼内的消防设备。
EN: The dormitory supervisor inspects the fire equipment in the dormitory building.

ZH: 舍监会帮助学生保管贵重物品。
EN: The dormitory supervisor helps students keep valuable items.

ZH: 学生需要尊重舍监的权威和建议。
EN: Students need to respect the authority and advice of the dormitory supervisor.

ZH: 舍监会组织宿舍楼的各类活动。
EN: The dormitory supervisor organizes various activities in the dormitory building.

ZH: 学生可以向舍监咨询学习方面的问题。
EN: Students can consult the dormitory supervisor about academic issues.

ZH: 舍监会帮助学生处理宿舍生活中的纠纷。
EN: The dormitory supervisor helps students resolve disputes in dormitory life.

ZH: 学生应该遵守舍监制定的宿舍纪律。
EN: Students should adhere to the dormitory discipline set by the dormitory supervisor.

ZH: 舍监是学生宿舍管理的重要角色。
EN: The dormitory supervisor is an important figure in student dormitory management.
